## Attribution and Contributor Anonymity

CanadaScanada publishes under an institutional voice. No individual contributor
names are exposed in published outputs per the project's contributor-anonymity
policy. Attribution of the corpus as a whole is to "CanadaScanada Editorial."

## Note on Source Materials

Source materials cited in `references/` records (articles, government releases,
academic papers) remain under the copyright of their original authors and
publishers. CanadaScanada records only the bibliographic metadata and
verification status of those sources; it does not reproduce their full text.
The CC BY 4.0 licence covers CanadaScanada's original data and editorial work,
not the underlying sources.
